# Clerk Authentication
# Get these from https://dashboard.clerk.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_YOUR_PUBLISHABLE_KEY
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_YOUR_SECRET_KEY

# Supabase - Database & Sync
# Get these from https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/_/settings/api
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_ID.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.YOUR_ANON_KEY

# =============================================================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. Clerk Setup:
#    - Create an app at https://dashboard.clerk.com
#    - Copy the publishable key and secret key above
#
# 2. Supabase Setup:
#    - Create a project at https://supabase.com
#    - Go to Project Settings > Data API to get the URL and anon key
#
# 3. Clerk-Supabase Integration (REQUIRED for cloud sync):
#    - In Clerk Dashboard: Go to https://dashboard.clerk.com/setup/supabase
#      and activate the Supabase integration
#    - In Supabase Dashboard: Go to Authentication > Sign In / Up > Add provider
#      and add Clerk with your Clerk domain
#
# 4. Run database migrations:
#    - cd supabase && supabase db push
#
# Without the Clerk-Supabase integration, the app will work in localStorage-only mode.
#
# =============================================================================

# Optional: Customize sign-in/sign-up redirects
